---

import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Our Faculty | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad"
	description="Meet the experienced, qualified faculty of Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College — Principal, Vice Principal, academic coordinators, and department heads."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
>
	  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Faculty</span></div>
      <h1>Our Faculty</h1>
      <p>Experienced, qualified educators who know every student by name — the heart of Saraswati Shiksha Niketan.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">School Leadership</span>
        <h2>Principal &amp; Vice Principal</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="max-width:800px;margin-inline:auto;">
        <div class="person-card reveal">
          <div class="person-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580894732444-8ecded7900cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Principal of the school" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
          <h4>Mrs. Sunita Sharma</h4>
          <p class="person-role">Principal</p>
          <p>M.A. Education, B.Ed. · 24 years in academic leadership · With the school since 2014.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="person-card reveal">
          <div class="person-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544717305-2782549b5136?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Vice Principal of the school" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
          <h4>Mr. Deepak Malhotra</h4>
          <p class="person-role">Vice Principal</p>
          <p>M.Sc. Mathematics, B.Ed. · 19 years teaching experience · With the school since 2009.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Guiding Every Level</span>
        <h2>Academic Coordinators</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="person-card card reveal">
          <div class="person-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580894908361-967195033215?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Primary wing academic coordinator" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
          <h4>Mrs. Anjali Verma</h4>
          <p class="person-role">Coordinator, Primary Wing</p>
          <p>B.El.Ed., M.A. Hindi · Oversees Nursery to Class 5.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="person-card card reveal">
          <div class="person-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Middle wing academic coordinator" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
          <h4>Mr. Rakesh Tomar</h4>
          <p class="person-role">Coordinator, Middle Wing</p>
          <p>M.Sc. Physics, B.Ed. · Oversees Class 6 to 8.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="person-card card reveal">
          <div class="person-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Senior wing academic coordinator" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
          <h4>Mrs. Neelam Chauhan</h4>
          <p class="person-role">Coordinator, Senior Wing</p>
          <p>M.A. English, B.Ed. · Oversees Class 9 to 12.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Subject Leadership</span>
        <h2>Department Heads</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 2v6.34a2 2 0 0 1-.24.96L3.6 18.4A2 2 0 0 0 5.36 21.5h13.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.76-3.1l-5.16-9.1a2 2 0 0 1-.24-.96V2"/><path d="M6.5 2h11"/><path d="M6.5 12.5h11"/></svg></div><h4>Mrs. Pooja Saxena</h4><p class="person-role">Head, Science Dept.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg></div><h4>Mr. Suresh Yadav</h4><p class="person-role">Head, Mathematics Dept.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div><h4>Mrs. Kiran Bhatt</h4><p class="person-role">Head, Languages Dept.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div><h4>Mr. Vivek Rana</h4><p class="person-role">Head, Commerce Dept.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">By the Numbers</span>
        <h2>Our Faculty at a Glance</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"><span data-counter="85" data-suffix="+">0</span></div><p>Total Faculty Members</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"><span data-counter="72" data-suffix="%">0</span></div><p>Post-Graduate Qualified</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"><span data-counter="12" data-suffix=" yrs">0</span></div><p>Average Teaching Experience</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"><span data-counter="100" data-suffix="%">0</span></div><p>B.Ed. / Trained Educators</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">How We Teach</span>
        <h2>Our Teaching Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="lede">We believe teaching is a relationship, not a transaction. Our faculty are trained to notice when a student is struggling long before it shows up on a report card, and to celebrate progress, not just perfection.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Every teacher completes annual professional development training</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Small-group attention within structured classroom sizes</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Open-door policy for parent-teacher communication</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Mentorship pairing for new and early-career teachers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571260899304-425eee4c7efc?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Teacher interacting with young students in class" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
